name: Man eating his child's flesh at moonlight
description:
#13 - Based on "Saturn devouring his son" by Peter Paul Rubens

Is evil real?

Aren't we animals trying to be gods?

These questions attempt to bring an individual closer to the idea of ​​cruelty

A cannibal man devours his son in front of his mother's eyes. Perhaps the Devil exists, and as an artist, he shows us the dark side of life, death
